headline: General Mills Expands Dec. 21, 2025, Voluntary Recall of Select Pillsbury Pizza Pops Products
summary: TORONTO, January 25, 2026--General Mills Expands Dec. 21, 2025, Voluntary Recall of Select Pillsbury Pizza Pops Products

headline: Minnesota Execs, Sports Teams Call on Authorities to Ease Tensions
summary: More than 60 leaders of Minnesota-based companies and sports teams signed a letter calling on federal, state and local officials to work together.  Executives from companies including 3M, Best Buy, General Mills, Target and UnitedHealth Group, and sports teams including the Minnesota Vikings and Timberwolves, signed the letter.

headline: Alex Pretti killing: Minnesota CEOs, including UnitedHealth, Target, call for 'immediate deescalation'
summary: The Trump administration has surged federal law enforcement to the city to enforce its immigration crackdown and pursue allegations of widespread welfare fraud.
